description:
It was discovered that GNU binutils contained a large number of security
issues. If a user or automated system were tricked into processing a
specially-crafted file, a remote attacker could cause GNU binutils to
crash, resulting in a denial of service, or possibly execute arbitrary
code.

binutils.description: GNU assembler, linker and binary utilities

title: GNU binutils vulnerabilities
action: In general, a standard system update will make all the necessary changes.
isummary: Several security issues were fixed in GNU binutils.
